text: Eroni Cama Talemaisolomoni Mawi (born 2 June 1996) is a Fijian rugby player for Fijian Latui in Global Rapid Rugby and the Fijian national team. His primary position is prop. In August 2019 he was named in Fiji's squad for the 2019 Rugby World Cup. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Fijian rugby union players Category:Rugby union props Category:Fiji international rugby union players
